* Compiliation on Win32:

 - Install Cygwin
 - Install MinGW
 - Download SDL development packages for MinGW (SDL-devel-1.2.5a-mingw32.tar.gz)
   + copy include files / libraries / aclocals / sdl-config in the appropriate directories
   + modify sdl.m4 !
   + (make sure SDL.dll is present)
   + install SDL_sound (copy SDL_sound.h into MinGW's include directory ./SDL)
   + install SDL_image (copy SDL_image.h into MinGW's include directory ./SDL)
(   + copy libSDL_sound.a into the /lib directory   (mv SDL_sound.lib libSDL_sound.a)
   + copy libSDL_image.a into the /lib directory
   + copy libvorbis.a into the /lib directory
   + copy libvorbisfile.a into the /lib directory)
   + install libsigc++ 1.0.3: see /dev

 - Download and install SDL_sound (SDL_sound-1.0.0.tar.gz)


(2003-05-13 Gregor Mitsch <gregormitsch@gmx.de>)
(2003-05-14 Gregor Mitsch <gregormitsch@gmx.de>)



